WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.480 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:09.430 align:middle line:90%


00:00:09.430 --> 00:00:10.841 align:middle line:84%
You know, you should
take a partner.

00:00:10.841 --> 00:00:11.540 align:middle line:90%
I'm ready.

00:00:11.540 --> 00:00:13.100 align:middle line:84%
I'm just waiting for
the right person.

00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:14.290 align:middle line:90%
What about me?

00:00:14.290 --> 00:00:15.050 align:middle line:90%
You're 65.

00:00:15.050 --> 00:00:15.990 align:middle line:90%
I'm 109.

00:00:15.990 --> 00:00:17.665 align:middle line:90%
It would be a disaster.

00:00:17.665 --> 00:00:19.480 align:middle line:84%
Besides, what about
the new guy, Ballion?

00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:20.560 align:middle line:90%
He's bi.

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:21.540 align:middle line:90%
Bi?

00:00:21.540 --> 00:00:23.440 align:middle line:90%
Yes, bi-humanoid.

00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:26.792 align:middle line:84%
He's one single soul
in two humanoid bodies.

00:00:26.792 --> 00:00:28.154 align:middle line:84%
[LAUGHS]
-That's nothing.

00:00:28.154 --> 00:00:29.320 align:middle line:84%
You see that all
the time nowadays.

00:00:29.320 --> 00:00:35.891 align:middle line:90%


00:00:35.891 --> 00:00:38.190 align:middle line:84%
EELA: Some say that the Akashic
Records will show humans

00:00:38.190 --> 00:00:40.630 align:middle line:84%
as filled with heart but
unaware of the Gift's

00:00:40.630 --> 00:00:41.380 align:middle line:90%
ultimate potential.

00:00:41.380 --> 00:00:43.046 align:middle line:84%
ENO: You know, I don't
really care what's recorded

00:00:43.046 --> 00:00:44.170 align:middle line:90%
in the Akashic Records.

00:00:44.170 --> 00:00:45.420 align:middle line:84%
No one even knows
where those are.

00:00:45.420 --> 00:00:47.210 align:middle line:84%
Have you ever seen them?
EELA: No.

00:00:47.210 --> 00:00:48.340 align:middle line:90%
That's the whole point.

00:00:48.340 --> 00:00:49.839 align:middle line:84%
You don't see them.
ENO: Mhm.

00:00:49.839 --> 00:00:57.450 align:middle line:90%


00:00:57.450 --> 00:00:59.480 align:middle line:84%
What is it about them
that draws you so?

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:02.480 align:middle line:84%
Their humor is like
nothing I've ever seen.

00:01:02.480 --> 00:01:04.440 align:middle line:90%
We have humor.

00:01:04.440 --> 00:01:06.400 align:middle line:84%
Name the funniest
being in our culture.

00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:07.650 align:middle line:90%
All right.

00:01:07.650 --> 00:01:10.120 align:middle line:90%
Miho.

00:01:10.120 --> 00:01:12.840 align:middle line:84%
ENO: Miho Carone is the funniest
being in our multiverse?

00:01:12.840 --> 00:01:14.220 align:middle line:90%
I believe so.

00:01:14.220 --> 00:01:15.630 align:middle line:84%
If that's true, throw
me into the Black

00:01:15.630 --> 00:01:17.530 align:middle line:90%
Hole of Orion right now.

00:01:17.530 --> 00:01:18.380 align:middle line:90%
I'm serious.

00:01:18.380 --> 00:01:20.410 align:middle line:84%
I'll disincorporate on
the spot and reemerge

00:01:20.410 --> 00:01:21.900 align:middle line:90%
into a culture with some irony.

00:01:21.900 --> 00:01:42.690 align:middle line:90%


00:01:42.690 --> 00:01:43.890 align:middle line:90%
Is that your mother?

00:01:43.890 --> 00:01:57.066 align:middle line:90%


00:01:57.066 --> 00:01:58.660 align:middle line:84%
Ballion, what are
you doing here?

00:01:58.660 --> 00:02:00.660 align:middle line:84%
I was awakened by a
vision of a journey.

00:02:00.660 --> 00:02:02.380 align:middle line:84%
One that you will not
be allowed to make.

00:02:02.380 --> 00:02:03.700 align:middle line:90%
What business is that of yours?

00:02:03.700 --> 00:02:05.450 align:middle line:90%
I'm managing this dialogue.

00:02:05.450 --> 00:02:07.210 align:middle line:84%
I've assigned Ballion
to this post because

00:02:07.210 --> 00:02:08.820 align:middle line:90%
of his intuitive abilities.

00:02:08.820 --> 00:02:10.400 align:middle line:84%
We are aware of
your mother figure's

00:02:10.400 --> 00:02:11.950 align:middle line:90%
fondness for the blue planet.

00:02:11.950 --> 00:02:13.220 align:middle line:90%
I'm also aware of her--

00:02:13.220 --> 00:02:15.330 align:middle line:84%
Unsuccessful mission
to plant the Gift.

00:02:15.330 --> 00:02:16.690 align:middle line:90%
It wasn't unsuccessful.

00:02:16.690 --> 00:02:18.490 align:middle line:84%
There are countless
shrines to the Gift.

00:02:18.490 --> 00:02:21.580 align:middle line:84%
Yes, but they have chosen not
to use it as it was intended.

00:02:21.580 --> 00:02:23.620 align:middle line:84%
I don't want to go up because
they're doing anything wrong.

00:02:23.620 --> 00:02:25.370 align:middle line:90%
Their use of the gift is unique.

00:02:25.370 --> 00:02:27.420 align:middle line:84%
Eno believes that a
descendant of the man

00:02:27.420 --> 00:02:30.740 align:middle line:84%
who received the Gift now
leaves in Recent Mexico.

00:02:30.740 --> 00:02:31.680 align:middle line:90%
New Mexico.

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:33.430 align:middle line:84%
I simply want to
meet her face-to-face

00:02:33.430 --> 00:02:36.020 align:middle line:84%
and share with her what
else the Gift is capable of.

00:02:36.020 --> 00:02:37.040 align:middle line:90%
That will not be condoned.

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:45.337 align:middle line:90%


00:02:45.337 --> 00:02:47.270 align:middle line:84%
BALLION A: You will not be
allowed to leave this chamber--

00:02:47.270 --> 00:02:48.436 align:middle line:84%
Until counsel can
be administered.

00:02:48.436 --> 00:02:54.100 align:middle line:90%


00:02:54.100 --> 00:02:57.770 align:middle line:84%
Eno, I offer my assistance.
Do you accept?

00:02:57.770 --> 00:03:10.500 align:middle line:90%


00:03:10.500 --> 00:03:12.310 align:middle line:84%
Because you are a
friend of Eela's--

00:03:12.310 --> 00:03:14.236 align:middle line:84%
I made an appeal, but
they would not give in.

00:03:14.236 --> 00:03:18.101 align:middle line:90%


00:03:18.101 --> 00:03:22.690 align:middle line:84%
-Tell me.
-Why are you so drawn to them?

00:03:22.690 --> 00:03:24.690 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:03:24.690 --> 00:04:13.460 align:middle line:90%


00:04:13.460 --> 00:04:14.760 align:middle line:90%
It's an umbrella.

00:04:14.760 --> 00:04:16.534 align:middle line:90%
It's quite useful.

00:04:16.534 --> 00:04:17.300 align:middle line:90%
Transmission incoming.

00:04:17.300 --> 00:04:19.870 align:middle line:90%


00:04:19.870 --> 00:04:21.160 align:middle line:90%
You know what happens to me--

00:04:21.160 --> 00:04:22.650 align:middle line:90%
If this is logged on my record.

00:04:22.650 --> 00:04:23.487 align:middle line:90%
It was my decision.

00:04:23.487 --> 00:04:24.800 align:middle line:90%
Mine alone.

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:25.860 align:middle line:90%
I will cover for you--

00:04:25.860 --> 00:04:27.250 align:middle line:90%
BALLION B: For Eela's sake.

00:04:27.250 --> 00:04:28.950 align:middle line:90%
EELA: Don't do me any favors.

00:04:28.950 --> 00:04:32.740 align:middle line:84%
And have fun with Zap, or
Zip, or whatever her name is.

00:04:32.740 --> 00:04:34.770 align:middle line:90%
Paz employs my services.

00:04:34.770 --> 00:04:36.050 align:middle line:90%
BALLION B: NOTHING else.

00:04:36.050 --> 00:04:37.220 align:middle line:84%
BALLION A: I will
cover for you--

00:04:37.220 --> 00:04:38.730 align:middle line:90%
For a limited time segment.

00:04:38.730 --> 00:04:40.160 align:middle line:90%
But under three conditions.

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:42.590 align:middle line:84%
Number one, you must
not reveal your origins.

00:04:42.590 --> 00:04:44.790 align:middle line:84%
BALLION A: Number two, you
must record your experiences

00:04:44.790 --> 00:04:46.150 align:middle line:90%
and transmit them to me.

00:04:46.150 --> 00:04:48.220 align:middle line:84%
And number three,
you must eat daily--

00:04:48.220 --> 00:04:50.010 align:middle line:84%
At the most popular
establishment--

00:04:50.010 --> 00:04:52.810 align:middle line:84%
Vouched for by 57
million inhabitants.

00:04:52.810 --> 00:04:55.330 align:middle line:84%
-Would you repeat number three?
-It's all right.

00:04:55.330 --> 00:04:58.880 align:middle line:90%
He's attempting to be humorous.

00:04:58.880 --> 00:05:01.960 align:middle line:84%
I'll also study Earth humor and
hope to discover their secret,

00:05:01.960 --> 00:05:03.175 align:middle line:90%
so that we may all benefit.

00:05:03.175 --> 00:05:07.632 align:middle line:90%


00:05:07.632 --> 00:05:10.092 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:05:10.092 --> 00:05:15.020 align:middle line:90%


00:05:15.020 --> 00:05:17.130 align:middle line:84%
May I see an image
of the descended one?

00:05:17.130 --> 00:05:17.830 align:middle line:90%
Certainly.

00:05:17.830 --> 00:05:20.850 align:middle line:90%
Access personal file 3901.

00:05:20.850 --> 00:05:22.610 align:middle line:90%
Her name is Bonnie.

00:05:22.610 --> 00:05:24.760 align:middle line:90%
Her location is not recorded.

00:05:24.760 --> 00:05:26.120 align:middle line:90%
No, it was not in the archives.

00:05:26.120 --> 00:05:28.980 align:middle line:84%
But according to my
research, her parents

00:05:28.980 --> 00:05:31.510 align:middle line:84%
lived right above a
local shrine to the Gift.

00:05:31.510 --> 00:05:34.000 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps Bonnie still
resides there, as well.

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:35.110 align:middle line:90%
Perhaps.

00:05:35.110 --> 00:05:36.560 align:middle line:90%
That's a nice touch.

00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:37.650 align:middle line:90%
Very human.

00:05:37.650 --> 00:05:40.493 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:05:40.493 --> 00:05:42.958 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:05:42.958 --> 00:05:48.874 align:middle line:90%


00:05:48.874 --> 00:05:50.510 align:middle line:84%
I'll have the
Happy Meal, please.

00:05:50.510 --> 00:05:54.172 align:middle line:90%


00:05:54.172 --> 00:05:57.900 align:middle line:84%
You don't have
to qualify for it.

00:05:57.900 --> 00:05:59.370 align:middle line:90%
Anything else?

00:05:59.370 --> 00:06:03.592 align:middle line:84%
The fruit and nut pack and
the apple pie for this one.

00:06:03.592 --> 00:06:05.584 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:06:05.584 --> 00:06:25.006 align:middle line:90%


00:06:25.006 --> 00:06:26.002 align:middle line:90%
Hey!

00:06:26.002 --> 00:06:26.998 align:middle line:90%
