00:06:37.812 --> 00:06:38.736 align:middle line:90%
[SMACK]

00:06:38.736 --> 00:06:39.660 align:middle line:90%
Ouch!

00:06:39.660 --> 00:06:40.710 align:middle line:90%
That is not necessary.

00:06:40.710 --> 00:06:41.510 align:middle line:90%
Easy, homeboy.

00:06:41.510 --> 00:06:43.310 align:middle line:84%
Girlfriend's just
showing you some love.

00:06:43.310 --> 00:06:45.700 align:middle line:84%
How would homegirl like a
kick in the digestive exit?

00:06:45.700 --> 00:06:46.590 align:middle line:90%
Study the brochures.

00:06:46.590 --> 00:06:48.180 align:middle line:90%
I'll inquire.

00:06:48.180 --> 00:06:50.104 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps we are in
search of a location.

00:06:50.104 --> 00:06:53.800 align:middle line:90%


00:06:53.800 --> 00:06:55.490 align:middle line:84%
I'm in the mood for
a little kickback.

00:06:55.490 --> 00:06:57.000 align:middle line:84%
Need to take my
mind off the moment

00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:59.310 align:middle line:90%
and spin the light fantastic.

00:06:59.310 --> 00:07:01.401 align:middle line:84%
Me and home-slice here
don't know where to look.

00:07:01.401 --> 00:07:02.100 align:middle line:90%
Oh.

00:07:02.100 --> 00:07:04.630 align:middle line:84%
Well, you can use
our computer kiosk.

00:07:04.630 --> 00:07:06.490 align:middle line:90%
Just google it.

00:07:06.490 --> 00:07:08.181 align:middle line:84%
This woman has
excellent advice.

00:07:08.181 --> 00:07:11.038 align:middle line:84%
Please, Eno.
Google.

00:07:11.038 --> 00:07:13.006 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:07:13.006 --> 00:07:19.402 align:middle line:90%


00:07:19.402 --> 00:07:21.862 align:middle line:90%
[GURGLING]

00:07:21.862 --> 00:07:37.471 align:middle line:90%


00:07:37.471 --> 00:07:38.170 align:middle line:90%
Find location.

00:07:38.170 --> 00:07:41.440 align:middle line:90%


00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:43.860 align:middle line:90%
Donde esta locaciones?

00:07:43.860 --> 00:07:45.490 align:middle line:90%
Find location.

00:07:45.490 --> 00:07:47.940 align:middle line:90%
(OVERENUNCIATING) Find location.

00:07:47.940 --> 00:07:49.020 align:middle line:90%
Find location.

00:07:49.020 --> 00:07:50.337 align:middle line:90%
Find location.

00:07:50.337 --> 00:07:53.610 align:middle line:90%
Don't you know how to type?

00:07:53.610 --> 00:07:57.415 align:middle line:84%
ENO: Search "Shrine
to the Gift."

00:07:57.415 --> 00:07:59.530 align:middle line:90%
