00:07:59.530 --> 00:08:03.758 align:middle line:84%
ENO: Try simply "movie theater."
WOMAN: Yep.

00:08:03.758 --> 00:08:05.234 align:middle line:10%
There you go.

00:08:05.234 --> 00:08:08.676 align:middle line:90%


00:08:08.676 --> 00:08:11.116 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:08:11.116 --> 00:08:14.021 align:middle line:90%


00:08:14.021 --> 00:08:15.420 align:middle line:84%
ENO: We have located
a shrine to the Gift,

00:08:15.420 --> 00:08:17.080 align:middle line:90%
the one we have been seeking.

00:08:17.080 --> 00:08:18.707 align:middle line:84%
We are en route to
its destination.

00:08:18.707 --> 00:08:23.580 align:middle line:90%


00:08:23.580 --> 00:08:25.330 align:middle line:84%
