00:08:30.490 --> 00:08:33.457 align:middle line:84%
We will investigate and
hope that the descended one

00:08:33.457 --> 00:08:34.156 align:middle line:90%
is nearby.

00:08:34.156 --> 00:08:39.080 align:middle line:90%


00:08:39.080 --> 00:08:40.030 align:middle line:90%
