00:08:51.630 --> 00:08:53.660 align:middle line:90%
That's because there isn't one.

00:08:53.660 --> 00:08:56.183 align:middle line:84%
Movie tickets, that
I can help you with.

00:08:56.183 --> 00:09:00.440 align:middle line:90%


00:09:00.440 --> 00:09:02.690 align:middle line:90%
Hit me one more time.

00:09:02.690 --> 00:09:04.231 align:middle line:84%
Then we'll have a deal.
Whoa.

00:09:04.231 --> 00:09:04.930 align:middle line:90%
Whoa!

00:09:04.930 --> 00:09:14.621 align:middle line:90%


00:09:14.621 --> 00:09:16.122 align:middle line:84%
It's all right.
It's just a mannequin.

00:09:16.122 --> 00:09:20.950 align:middle line:90%


00:09:20.950 --> 00:09:22.940 align:middle line:90%
Welcome to "Casablanca" Week.

00:09:22.940 --> 00:09:24.550 align:middle line:84%
Our problems don't
amount to a hill

00:09:24.550 --> 00:09:26.280 align:middle line:90%
of beans in this crazy world.

00:09:26.280 --> 00:09:27.020 align:middle line:90%
Don't be afraid.

00:09:27.020 --> 00:09:28.400 align:middle line:84%
I think this will
be the beginning

00:09:28.400 --> 00:09:30.710 align:middle line:90%
of a very beautiful friendship.

00:09:30.710 --> 00:09:33.160 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:09:33.160 --> 00:09:42.470 align:middle line:90%


00:09:42.470 --> 00:09:44.440 align:middle line:84%
What can you do
in the present that

00:09:44.440 --> 00:09:46.710 align:middle line:84%
will inspire this Earth
woman to understand

00:09:46.710 --> 00:09:48.310 align:middle line:90%
the Gift's potential?

00:09:48.310 --> 00:09:50.340 align:middle line:90%
What can we do?

00:09:50.340 --> 00:09:51.990 align:middle line:90%
Yes, home-slice.

00:09:51.990 --> 00:09:53.955 align:middle line:90%
What can we do?

00:09:53.955 --> 00:09:54.920 align:middle line:90%
Whatever's necessary.

00:09:54.920 --> 00:09:58.420 align:middle line:90%


00:09:58.420 --> 00:10:00.479 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:10:00.479 --> 00:10:18.460 align:middle line:90%


