00:10:58.080 --> 00:11:02.280 align:middle line:84%
You have absolutely
nothing to be sorry about.

00:11:02.280 --> 00:11:04.086 align:middle line:90%
We've been here how many times?

00:11:04.086 --> 00:11:05.380 align:middle line:90%
It's--

00:11:05.380 --> 00:11:08.610 align:middle line:84%
