I gotta go.
-Yuka?

00:25:24.760 --> 00:25:27.520 align:middle line:90%


00:25:27.520 --> 00:25:29.040 align:middle line:84%
BETSY (VOICEOVER): Dear
Hailee, I know you're

00:25:29.040 --> 00:25:31.280 align:middle line:90%
