00:25:41.370 --> 00:25:43.110 align:middle line:90%
I don't want Mom to worry.

00:25:43.110 --> 00:25:46.148 align:middle line:84%
And you're the
smartest woman I know.

00:25:46.148 --> 00:25:47.136 align:middle line:90%
What is it?

00:25:47.136 --> 00:25:57.016 align:middle line:90%


00:25:57.016 --> 00:25:58.992 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:25:58.992 --> 00:26:18.752 align:middle line:90%


00:26:18.752 --> 00:26:20.710 align:middle line:90%
Leave it on.

00:26:20.710 --> 00:26:21.971 align:middle line:90%
I want you to film it.

00:26:21.971 --> 00:26:26.390 align:middle line:90%


00:26:26.390 --> 00:26:34.570 align:middle line:84%
I've raised money, stayed
up for weeks at a time,

00:26:34.570 --> 00:26:41.740 align:middle line:84%
divorced my husband, neglected
my health and those close

00:26:41.740 --> 00:26:44.460 align:middle line:90%
to me.

00:26:44.460 --> 00:26:46.860 align:middle line:84%
But I did it because
I was after something.

00:26:46.860 --> 00:26:53.354 align:middle line:84%
I never cried, never
complained, because I'm a doer.

00:26:53.354 --> 00:26:59.920 align:middle line:84%
[LAUGHS] And the one
thing I've always wanted

00:26:59.920 --> 00:27:07.687 align:middle line:84%
is the one thing I need to
save my goddaughter's life.

00:27:07.687 --> 00:27:09.683 align:middle line:90%
And I don't have it.

00:27:09.683 --> 00:27:22.791 align:middle line:90%


00:27:22.791 --> 00:27:24.290 align:middle line:84%
ENO (VOICEOVER): In a
way, you are collecting

00:27:24.290 --> 00:27:28.190 align:middle line:84%
all images, all
emotions, the way it is

00:27:28.190 --> 00:27:29.830 align:middle line:90%
and the way you'd like it to be.

00:27:29.830 --> 00:27:33.080 align:middle line:84%
Then, if you choose,
use the Gift to focus

00:27:33.080 --> 00:27:34.670 align:middle line:90%
