00:27:34.670 --> 00:27:35.690 align:middle line:90%
Just follow your intuition.

00:27:35.690 --> 00:27:37.371 align:middle line:84%
You'll be fine.
-OK.

00:27:37.371 --> 00:27:41.404 align:middle line:90%


00:27:41.404 --> 00:27:43.348 align:middle line:90%
They're spying on us.

00:27:43.348 --> 00:27:48.710 align:middle line:90%


00:27:48.710 --> 00:27:50.650 align:middle line:84%
There's something I
should have told you.

00:27:50.650 --> 00:27:52.160 align:middle line:90%
I am connected to this human.

00:27:52.160 --> 00:27:56.400 align:middle line:90%


00:27:56.400 --> 00:27:59.030 align:middle line:84%
It was my parent figure that
brought the Gift to Earth.

00:27:59.030 --> 00:28:02.180 align:middle line:90%
EELA: Yes, I know.

00:28:02.180 --> 00:28:05.460 align:middle line:84%
ENO: There's something else my
family's chosen not to share.

00:28:05.460 --> 00:28:09.898 align:middle line:84%
There was an encounter, the
nature of which was unexpected.

00:28:09.898 --> 00:28:13.670 align:middle line:90%


00:28:13.670 --> 00:28:15.066 align:middle line:84%
Bonnie and I are of
the same lineage.

00:28:15.066 --> 00:28:20.900 align:middle line:90%


00:28:20.900 --> 00:28:23.000 align:middle line:84%
I want you to
try something now.

