For the next couple minutes,
I want you to talk only

00:28:25.850 --> 00:28:27.900 align:middle line:84%
about what you want
to see in your life,

00:28:27.900 --> 00:28:33.800 align:middle line:84%
as if you could wave a magic
wand and create anything.

00:28:33.800 --> 00:28:36.540 align:middle line:84%
I see my entire
staff reinstated,

00:28:36.540 --> 00:28:39.910 align:middle line:84%
and they all have their own
personalized parking spots.

00:28:39.910 --> 00:28:43.120 align:middle line:84%
