balls that symbolize

00:28:43.120 --> 00:28:44.730 align:middle line:90%
our passionate hearts.

00:28:44.730 --> 00:28:49.790 align:middle line:84%
I see a picture in my mind
of myself at my very best.

00:28:49.790 --> 00:28:53.010 align:middle line:84%
A fearless heart that resonates
with an endless passion

00:28:53.010 --> 00:28:53.990 align:middle line:90%
to create.

00:28:53.990 --> 00:28:56.390 align:middle line:10%
And with a little
coaching from my director,

00:28:56.390 --> 00:28:58.880 align:middle line:10%
I realize this is who I am.

00:28:58.880 --> 00:29:03.250 align:middle line:84%
So I hold this self-portrait
of positivity in my heart.

00:29:03.250 --> 00:29:12.300 align:middle line:84%
And I, um, honor myself for
my beauty and my strength.

00:29:12.300 --> 00:29:13.770 align:middle line:90%
Wow.

00:29:13.770 --> 00:29:21.670 align:middle line:84%
The moment I said that, I
felt a rush of possibilities,

00:29:21.670 --> 00:29:25.920 align:middle line:84%
as if there was an
unlimited potential.

00:29:25.920 --> 00:29:30.190 align:middle line:84%
And it was here, right
here, the whole time.

00:29:30.190 --> 00:29:37.580 align:middle line:90%


00:29:37.580 --> 00:29:39.013 align:middle line:84%
Eno, there's a
message from Ballion.

00:29:39.013 --> 00:29:44.981 align:middle line:90%


00:29:44.981 --> 00:29:47.380 align:middle line:84%
It's all right.
It's just a painting.

00:29:47.380 --> 00:29:50.210 align:middle line:84%
I was in your quarters
monitoring your progress.

00:29:50.210 --> 00:29:51.860 align:middle line:84%
I was there longer
than expected and--

00:29:51.860 --> 00:29:53.620 align:middle line:90%
Security Console found me.

00:29:53.620 --> 00:29:55.100 align:middle line:84%
Your actions are
no longer a secret.

00:29:55.100 --> 00:29:56.750 align:middle line:84%
If you do not
return immediately--

00:29:56.750 --> 00:29:59.130 align:middle line:84%
You will be extracted with
or without your consent.

00:29:59.130 --> 00:30:02.300 align:middle line:84%
Ballion, why were you in
Eno's quarters for so long?

00:30:02.300 --> 00:30:03.080 align:middle line:90%
I watched--

00:30:03.080 --> 00:30:06.200 align:middle line:90%
Two of your Earth cinemas.

00:30:06.200 --> 00:30:06.900 align:middle line:90%
Which ones?

00:30:06.900 --> 00:30:09.051 align:middle line:84%
A cinematic set
simply entitled--

00:30:09.051 --> 00:30:10.810 align:middle line:84%
-"Rocky."
-Yes.

00:30:10.810 --> 00:30:13.340 align:middle line:84%
The one least
likely to succeed--

00:30:13.340 --> 00:30:15.090 align:middle line:90%
Rose up and became champion--

00:30:15.090 --> 00:30:15.990 align:middle line:90%
Of the world.

00:30:15.990 --> 00:30:18.370 align:middle line:84%
It was his inner strength that
propelled him like a rocket.

00:30:18.370 --> 00:30:19.760 align:middle line:90%
He kind of reminds me of you.

00:30:19.760 --> 00:30:21.250 align:middle line:90%
Interesting that you say that.

00:30:21.250 --> 00:30:23.880 align:middle line:84%
Because when they spoke
of Eye of the Tiger--

00:30:23.880 --> 00:30:25.746 align:middle line:90%
I felt it inside.

00:30:25.746 --> 00:30:31.400 align:middle line:84%
-[LAUGHS] Yes, I'm sure you did.
-Are you--

00:30:31.400 --> 00:30:32.880 align:middle line:90%
Laughing?

00:30:32.880 --> 00:30:35.390 align:middle line:84%
Yes, you're very funny
when you're inspired.

00:30:35.390 --> 00:30:36.610 align:middle line:90%
Eye of the Tiger.

00:30:36.610 --> 00:30:38.100 align:middle line:90%
And funny.

00:30:38.100 --> 00:30:39.178 align:middle line:90%
It is a new day.

00:30:39.178 --> 00:30:42.250 align:middle line:90%


00:30:42.250 --> 00:30:44.140 align:middle line:84%
I believe you were
caught in a solar storm.

00:30:44.140 --> 00:30:45.620 align:middle line:90%
It can't be helped.

00:30:45.620 --> 00:30:46.810 align:middle line:90%
Or circumnavigated.

00:30:46.810 --> 00:30:48.750 align:middle line:90%
The heat is simply too great.

00:30:48.750 --> 00:30:50.425 align:middle line:84%
But I will report your
return is imminent.

00:30:50.425 --> 00:31:03.130 align:middle line:90%


00:31:03.130 --> 00:31:05.122 align:middle line:84%
Are you sure you don't
want the big room?

00:31:05.122 --> 00:31:06.616 align:middle line:90%
No, this is lovely.

00:31:06.616 --> 00:31:08.608 align:middle line:90%
I like this one.

00:31:08.608 --> 00:31:09.620 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:31:09.620 --> 00:31:11.150 align:middle line:84%
I want you to stay
as long as you like.

00:31:11.150 --> 00:31:13.150 align:middle line:90%
Thank you, Marcia.

00:31:13.150 --> 00:31:15.650 align:middle line:10%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

