00:32:22.380 --> 00:32:24.300 align:middle line:84%
I wish more women could
see that in themselves.

00:32:24.300 --> 00:32:26.610 align:middle line:84%
I affirm my fearless
heart that resonates

00:32:26.610 --> 00:32:29.490 align:middle line:84%
with and endless passion
to create. [LAUGHS]

00:32:29.490 --> 00:32:32.350 align:middle line:84%
MARCIA: You know, when I read
about your life and your work,

00:32:32.350 --> 00:32:34.670 align:middle line:84%
