lens, too, if you want.

00:32:50.960 --> 00:32:52.040 align:middle line:90%
WILLIAM: OK.

00:32:52.040 --> 00:32:52.850 align:middle line:90%
Hello, Hailee.

00:32:52.850 --> 00:32:54.470 align:middle line:90%
