ENO (VOICEOVER): We
will miss you, as well.

00:35:59.670 --> 00:36:17.699 align:middle line:90%


00:36:17.699 --> 00:36:18.398 align:middle line:90%
Bye-bye.

00:36:18.398 --> 00:36:39.726 align:middle line:90%


