deeper, to laugh harder,

00:36:58.050 --> 00:37:00.700 align:middle line:84%
to live at the highest
possible vibration.

00:37:00.700 --> 00:37:04.700 align:middle line:84%
We will miss them, but we
will carry them in our hearts.

